# Harness rules (Cursor)

Read and follow `AGENTS.md` at repo root for full project context.

## Required session flow

1. Run `bash scripts/init.sh` before feature work
2. Read `PROGRESS.md` and `feature_list.json`
3. Work on exactly one open feature
4. Run all verification commands in AGENTS.md before done
5. Update PROGRESS.md and SESSION_HANDOFF.md at session end

## Constraints

- Do not claim done without verification evidence
- Do not edit feature_list.json to weaken acceptance criteria
- Prefer minimal, focused diffs
